      <h2>The 2018 Conference</h2>
      <p>
        The second edition of EISS took place on 21–22 June 2018 at the University Panthéon-Assas
        (Paris 2), in collaboration with the Centre Thucydide and the Center for Studies and
        Research on Administrative and Political Science (CERSA) of Paris 2. The detailed programme
        is preserved below.
      </p>
