      <h2>The 2017 Inaugural Conference</h2>
      <p>
        The EISS annual conference is organised by the Association for the Study of War and
        Strategy (AEGES). Its inaugural session took place on 13–14 January 2017 at the University
        Panthéon-Assas (Paris 2), in collaboration with the Centre Thucydide and the Center for
        Studies and Research on Administrative and Political Science (CERSA) of Paris 2.
      </p>
